Introduction Alpaca Cup is an event management application for hosting and scoring competitions. So far the app has been used exclusively for waterboarding competitions in Singapore, however we hope that it may be used in other extreme sports in the future (such as skateboarding) or indeed any competition that has a suitable format.
The App serves 2 main purposes;
